IMAGEMASH
by pops

Imagemash is an image batch processor developed with Python an Qt.

It is released under the GNU GPL V3
It is under development.
There are 4 plug-in now:
    a crop plug-in
    a resize plug-in
    a flip/rotate plug-in
    a free rotate plug-in

You can use it alone or with nautilus or thunar.

Nautilus:
use the script shell "imagemash-nautilus"

Thunar:
edit/custom action/add
and copy the following command: "python3 /path/to/imagemash.py %F"
or "xterm -hold -e "python3 /media/donnees/programation/imagemash/imagemash.py %F"" to start it in a terminal